      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON PASTIZZI (8) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 390m behind Nacho Problem (22.88) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Better than last start and worth following up. MORAINE DAMIAN (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (26.36) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Should be in this for a long way. SMOOTH TIGER (1) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 8 last time (24.93) at Sale. Has won two of four starts from this draw. Overdue and is among the main hopes. STREET SIXTY SIX (7) is building a nice sequence of placings and will be in the mix again.",
